Dependencies :
===============

- Python 2.6 (or higher, but not compatible with 3.X)

If you need to provide output for MadEvent (not available under windows)
you will face the following dependencies:
- bash
- perl 5.8 (or higher)

On All Platform :
=================

If you need full functionality with MadEvent, you should install the
MG5 directory in the MG_ME directory (version 4.4.44 or later) with
the name \"madgraph5\".

On Windows:
===========

In order to run MG5 you should
1) add Python directory to the PATH
2) run $> python ./bin/mg5
